                     <summary>Written by or for <persName role="scr fmo" key="person_5160">John Wycham</persName>, monk of St. Leonard's priory, Norwich. (<ref target="https://catalog.hathitrust.org/Record/000468709">Pächt and Alexander</ref> iii. 970, pl. XCII). Initials and borders at the beginning of the Hours of the Lady office and the main parts of the book (fols. 8, 15, 29v, 36, 38, 41, 43, 50, etc.)</summary>
